          480,
          158,
          855,
          180
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "With the new Smallpdf experience, you can freely upload, organize, and share digital documents. When you enable the 'Storage' option, we'll also store all processed files here. ",
