      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Access Files Anytime, Anywhere ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
          480,
          570,
          815,
          590
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You can access files stored on Smallpdf from your computer, phone, or tablet. We'll also sync files from the Smallpdf Mobile App to our online portal ",
        "bbox": [
          478,
          599,
          937,
          690
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Collaborate With Others ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
          84,
          800,
          341,
          819
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Forget mundane administrative tasks. With Smallpdf, you can request e-signatures, send large files, or even enable the Smallpdf G Suite App for your entire organization. ",
